('content:4:4','a:5:{s:10:\"field_body\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"value\";s:1446:\"<p>In <strong>one business day</strong> this could be your website. <em>No really, it could...</em> <strong>Watershed Now!</strong> is a free and open source <a href=\"http://drupal.org\" target=\"_blank\">Drupal</a> distribution developed to support the common content management, social media, online advocacy, fundraising, and geo-mapping needs of conservation organizations, such as watershed groups, land trusts, and environmental chapter organizations.</p><p>Out of the box, Watershed Now! packs a punch - with all the tools your organization needs to quickly build its presence online. As your organization grows, Watershed Now! serves as a great platform for quickly and affordably building out a more customized website with beautiful graphic design and powerful messaging.</p><p>To learn more about Watershed Now!, you&#39;re best off just taking this demo site for a test drive. Click around and see what Watershed Now! can do. If you like it, we can <a href=\"/contact\">schedule you a tour</a> of the backend administrative interface. (It&#39;s really easy to drive this application, and we know you are going to love it.)</p><p>A complete listing of Watershed Now!&#39;s features can be found on our <a href=\"http://drupal.org/project/watershednow\" target=\"_blank\">Drupal.org project page</a>. To download your own copy of Watershed Now!, check us out on <a href=\"http://github.com/thinkshout/watershednow\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>.</p>\";s:6:\"format\";s:1:\"2\";}}s:18:\"field_get_involved\";a:5:{i:0;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:1;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:2;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:3;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:4;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}}s:13:\"field_sidebar\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"value\";s:444:\"<p><strong>Wondering if Watershed Now! can really help you build a website in a day?</strong></p><p>Check out our next upcoming <a href=\"http://cwf-websprint.waterwordsthatwork.com/\" target=\"_blank\">&quot;Website Sprint&quot; at the Chesapeake Bay Watershed Forum</a>, brought to you by <a href=\"http://waterwordsthatwork.com\" target=\"_blank\">Water Words That Work</a> and <a href=\"http://thinkshout.com\" target=\"_blank\">ThinkShout.com</a>.</p>\";s:6:\"format\";s:1:\"2\";}}s:17:\"field_attachments\";a:1:{i:0;N;}s:18:\"field_image_assets\";a:1:{i:0;N;}}',0,1283557255,'',1),('content:9:9','a:6:{s:12:\"field_teaser\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:\"value\";s:74:\"Check out this sample petion to see how our legislative lookup tool works.\";}}s:10:\"field_body\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"value\";s:505:\"<p>[This is a sample &quot;Take Action&quot; e-petition. Your submissions will not be sent to anyone, so feel free to play.]</p><h2>Save the Internet, Save the World!</h2><p>Well, actually this is a real campaign issue for us geeks. If you are curious sometime, check out NTEN&#39;s updates on <a href=\"http://www.nten.org/blog/2010/04/30/save-internet-save-world\" target=\"_blank\">Net Neutrality</a>. But for now, just have fun with the form below. We aren&#39;t going to send your responses anywhere.</p>\";s:6:\"format\";s:1:\"2\";}}s:18:\"field_get_involved\";a:5:{i:0;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:1;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:2;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:3;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}i:4;a:1:{s:3:\"nid\";N;}}s:13:\"field_sidebar\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"value\";N;s:6:\"format\";N;}}s:17:\"field_attachments\";a:1:{i:0;N;}s:18:\"field_image_assets\";a:1:{i:0;N;}}',0,1283558333,'',1);
